import { Card, Col, Row } from 'antd';

const AddressCard = () => (
  <Row gutter={16}>
    <Col span={8}>
      <Card title="Your Address" bordered={false}>
        Card content
      </Card>
    </Col>
    <Col span={8}>
      <Card title="Owner Address" bordered={false}>
        Card content
      </Card>
    </Col>
    <Col span={8}>
      <Card title="Counterparty Address" bordered={false}>
        Card content
      </Card>
    </Col>
  </Row>
);
export default AddressCard;
